<p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;">乌镇，中国江南水乡古镇的典型代表，曾名乌墩和青墩，位于</span><a href="http://you.ctrip.com/place/zhejiang100065.html" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204); text-decoration: none; font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;">浙江</a><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;">省</span><a href="http://you.ctrip.com/place/tongxiang220.html" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204); text-decoration: none; font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;">桐乡</a><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;">市北端，是国家5A级景区，拥有7000多年文明史和1300多年建镇史，素有“中国最后的枕水人家”的美誉，是我国二十个黄金周预报景点及江南六大古镇之一。乌镇有“鱼米之乡，丝绸之府”之称。千</span><a href="http://you.ctrip.com/food/yanbian415/30589.html" class="s_restaurant" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(0, 102, 204); text-decoration: none; font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;">百年</a><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px;">来，古镇民居临河而建、傍桥而市，镇内民风纯朴，除了拥有小桥、流水、人家的水乡风情和精巧雅致的民居建筑之外，更有着深厚的历史和浓郁的文化气息</span><br /><img src="http://youimg1.c-ctrip.com/target/tg/515/517/050/fb2a102930354c8b9b41eab69f2e7ce2.jpg" alt="" /><br /></p><p><img src="pictures/pictures/2013/12/9/1386577262349.jpg" alt="" /></p>